platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Theres something beautifully simple about lifting weights. Being able to see and feel your progress in what you can liftor how many times you can lift itis as straightforward as it comes. Enter Fitbod, the data-based weight-lifting app that makes logging your exercises as simple as lifting the actual dumbbell.
